Package com.bteam.common.models

Class CharacterDataModel

java.lang.Object
com.bteam.common.models.CharacterDataModel
public class CharacterDataModel extends Object
Data model for character entities

This class represents a Character Model to model characters. It contains static attributes about a character, including all movement and attack patterns as arrays of PatternModel

      public CharacterDataModel(String name, String description, int health, int attackPower, PatternService[] attackPatterns, PatternService[] movementPatterns, String attackDescription, String movementDescription)
      Creates a new CharacterDataModel.
      Parameters:
      name - name of the character
      description - a description for the character
      health - the health of the character
      attackPower - the power of the characters attack
      attackPatterns - all attack patterns that the character can perform
      movementPatterns - the movement pattern that the character can perform
      attackDescription - description of the attackPattern
      movementDescription - description of the movementPattern
